{"about_the_game":"<i>**Dreams of Sand is still in development - footage, screenshots etc. are not necessarily representative of the final version of the game.**</i><br>Dreams of Sand is a narrative-driven 3D block-pushing puzzle game. You play as Reverie, or Rev for short, a scientist struggling to formulate a cure for their lifelong disease, dreaming about their past, present and future.<br><br>Navigate and solve 50+ puzzles by pushing blocks, manipulating time and navigating small grid-based spaces in dreamy desert environments based on various locations from Reverie\u2019s life.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031160/extras/superpush1.gif?t=1734646724\" /><br><br>Explore the memories of a person's life from childhood to present day. Decide how they remember the events from their past, affecting who they are in the present and who they may become long into the future.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Tightly designed Grid-Based Puzzles</strong> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031160/extras/FallGracefullyAnim.gif?t=1734646724\" /><br><br></li><li><strong>Vibrant 3D Visuals</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031160/extras/PorticoTurnaround.gif?t=1734646724\" /><br><br></li><li><strong>Short-Story with Branching Choices</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031160/extras/SelectingChoices.gif?t=1734646724\" /></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031160/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734646724","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031160/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1734646724","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031160/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=173